autifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-156x234.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201333%202000\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients-for-a-grasshopper-cocktail\"\u003eIngredients for a Grasshopper Cocktail:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCrème de menthe:\u003c/strong\u003e The vibrant green crème de menthe is what gives this cocktail its amazing color and mint flavors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCrème de cacao:\u003c/strong\u003e This white liqueur brings the chocolate note to the drink with its buttery mouthfeel and sweet cacao profile.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHeavy cream:\u003c/strong\u003e This is what gives the grasshopper its thick and creamy base and gives it that dessert-in-a-glass decadence. You can also use half-and half as a slightly less rich option.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile you can use any glass for a grasshopper, it’s traditionally served in a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3XDkCB9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003ecoupe\u003c/a\u003e style or \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3MXgXJl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003emartini glass\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1727205320044\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eCan you use milk for a grasshopper instead of heavy cream?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eWhile heavy cream creates the creamiest version of a grasshopper, milk can be used in a pinch or if you find the heavy cream too rich for your liking. A higher fat content milk (like a whole milk) will create a creamier drink than a lower fat option like skim or 1% milk.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/grasshopper-cocktail/?tp_image_id=132162\" data-pin-title=\"grasshopper cocktail\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-co