12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-2.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-make-a-frozen-grasshopper\"\u003eHow to Make a Frozen Grasshopper:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA frozen grasshopper cocktail is quite possibly the most delicious boozy milkshake option ever. To make this, you simply swap the 1 ounce of heavy whipping cream for 1 cup of vanilla ice cream and blend in a blender until just smooth with the perfect milkshake consistency.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs you can tell from the ingredients, this is a very decadent and flavorful drink. Perfect for a holiday celebration!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-other-grasshopper-drink-variations\"\u003eOther Grasshopper Drink Variations:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFlying Grasshopper:\u003c/strong\u003e While the recipe for a Flying Grasshopper varies a bit, you make the drink “flying” by adding an once of vodka either in addition to the regular ingredients, or as a substitution for the heavy cream. Try using vanilla vodka for an added note of vanilla!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIrish Grasshopper:\u003c/strong\u003e Try adding a shot of Irish cream to the original recipe for a delicious St. Patrick’s Day twist.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/grasshopper-cocktail/?tp_image_id=132161\" data-pin-title=\"grasshopper cocktail\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5.jpg\" alt=\"grasshopper cocktail drink\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-156x234.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201333%202000\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5-156x234.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/grasshopper-cocktail-easy-best-drink-recipe-1-5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-and-tricks\"\u003eTips and tricks:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor a festive look, add a mini candy cane to the side of the glass.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eTry garnishing with a few chocolate shavings (or chocolate sprinkles) and fresh mint.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eKeep your glasses in the freezer before using for extra frosty containers.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eFor some extra chocolate taste, add chocolate sauce to the rim or drizzled inside the glass before pouring in your cocktail.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eTry serving it at a Halloween party to make use of its fun green color and frothy tops.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eP.S. If you love this drink, try a \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/brandy-alexander/\"\u003eBrandy Alexander\u003c/a\u003e or check out \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/20-delicious-cocktails/\"\u003e50+ Fun Cocktails to Make at Home\u003c/a\u003e for more recipes!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-more-recipes-to-try\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore Recipes to Try\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDips\u003c/strong\u003e – \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/homemade-french-onion-dip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eFrench Onion Dip\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/corn-dip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eCorn Dip\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/taco-dip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eTaco Dip\u003c/a\u003e\u